| Tier | Standard | `--quick` (critical friction only), `--exhaustive` (all friction) |
| Output dir | `.gstack/ux-audit/` | `Output to /tmp/ux` |

**Tiers determine which friction points get fixed:**
- **Quick:** Fix critical friction only (score 0 — dead ends, blocked workflows)
- **Standard:** + poor friction (score 0-1) (default)
- **Exhaustive:** + minor friction (score 0-2, everything below excellent)

